    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks. Regarding that review process, if the encroachment is very minor—say only a few inches—does the city typically allow for a variance, or is it strictly enforced? I'm trying to figure out if we can negotiate the boundary line or if the encroachment is an automatic disqualifier for the permit.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
